<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Verify Your Account - Greenmon</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333;">
    <h2>Welcome to Greenmon!</h2>
    <p>Hi <%= name %></p>
    <p>
        Thank you for signing up. To complete your registration, 
        please verify your account by clicking the button below:
    </p>
    <p style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <a 
            href="<%= link %>"
            style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;"
        >Verify Account</a>
    </p>
    <p>If you did not sign up for Greenmon, you may safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">Warm regards,<br />The Greenmon Team</p>
</body>

</html>